-	 *	 entity have the same weight on all CPUs. If the group
-	 *	 has 2 of its tasks on CPU0 and 1 task on CPU1, then a
-	 *	 better distribution of weight could be:
-	 *
-	 *	tg_A->se[0]->load.weight = 2/3 * 2000 = 1333
